features: ✎★ Powerful Performance: Manufactured from a durable plastic body, this compact washing machine is ideal for camping trips, dorms, apartments or anywhere with limited space. With 240W washing power and 120W spinner power, this washing machine works highly efficiently. Plastic body ensures this washing machine will never be rust eaten. Always quiet and clean.

✎★Large Capacity: With the Twin Tub dual function design, this washing machine can save your precious time by washing and spinning dry loads at the same time. You can tansfer clothes directly from the washer to the spinner – or run both together. If your room is not so spacious and you would like to have our washing machine.

✎★Time/Space-Saving: The strong and durable Portable Washing Machines features two tubs 1 for washing and 1 for spinning. Our two-tub-washing machine has 10 pounds of washing capacity and 7 pounds of spinning capacity.

✎★Considerable design: This compact mini twin tub washing machine is perfect for those with a need to multi-task, saving space and who may want to save themselves a trip to the expensive laundromat.This washing machine has separate timer control settings for washer and spinner operations: 15 minutes for washing and 5 minutes for spinning.

✎★Built-in Drain Pump: Built-in drain pump drains dirty water by more longer drainage tube from washer. This twin tub washing machine has a 1700rpm powerful motor with a maximum frequency of 60Hz. Save time, wash cleaner! The operation panel design of washing machine is simple, cleaning timing, rotating timing, more convenient to use.
